{"tid":2081424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post]今日要令港人港地收皮","createTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T15:25:45.000Z","uid":333890,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbea0514062bc3f74bbf2bb081dc8a6361aedee","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍營</span>皮，<span style=\"color: gold;\">人人</span>有責。</span><br />\n今日嘅目標係藍屍集中營<span style=\"color: red;\">港人港地</span>，目的令佢close page。<br />\n<br />\n今次任務行動有兩個:<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 檢舉(Report)。</span></span><br />\n記住記住一定要檢舉而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span></span>派嬲/留言，因為根據Facebook演算法會將個page recommend比更多人睇，變咗免費宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常大家會用mobile version，先㩒呢個options掣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FM2OZ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FM2OZ3.png&h=bfb91447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/372QXTB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F372QXTB.png&h=2a798ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後選擇report category。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75rFAFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75rFAFm.png&h=9dfc6330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小孩子才做選擇，一個人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以多次檢舉</span></span>唔同category(尤其係hate speech: Facebook依家加強對hate speech嘅審查，可借力打力)<br />\n本人做哂全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 檢查自己有冇唔小心like個page。</span></span><br />\n一幅圖話你知點解:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tyo8KyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyo8KyS.png&h=0279aaf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連高質page如香港黑警都冇咁多，<strong>請將你嘅姆指放係正確地方</strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtAyVF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtAyVF2.png&h=3123c8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次行動最好係廁所/食飯/搭車/百般無聊時執行。<br />\n祝各位網軍武運昌隆。"},{"pid":"e308e32bf79f7c320251204375f452d1f6c6c91d","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"推一"},{"pid":"e337cd76432f0e853c536cca55f82d6ae4b69587","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"874e156d66653b95fc4d9b44128c9301671337e9","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"8721d10886e5ca8d122de526785bb860619c1ac7","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"推四"},{"pid":"5f236954865cc3a091631a3a8b9b2117149879da","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"推五"},{"pid":"4f008507fb7feb625e967e30b31700d66935f191","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"推六"},{"pid":"52b11f1393bebd3cb2f0ba4f8c03c4bf1780587d","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"推七"},{"pid":"cb319fd63baac2958c8e56391aba34869f8580ed","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"推八"},{"pid":"6fba28bac9521e20f8bfb5669cef719a470e0efb","tid":2081424,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"推九"},{"pid":"ce5ad9368a0ab9019eb977fbe67f6475d7ba3b8f","tid":2081424,"uid"